videos.description: Tyus Battle blows by his defender and gets the tough and-1 layup to fall despite the contact.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Battle bangs through lane for score

videos.description: Paschal Chukwu gets the lob from Frank Howard and stuffs home the two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Cuse's Chukwu throws down alley-oop

videos.description: Wake Forest head coach Danny Manning credits his defense for getting his team back into the game after a slow start.
videos.headline: Manning happy with way team fought back

videos.description: Marek Dolezaj gets the dish from Paschal Chukwu and drops in the easy basket for the Orange.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Dolezaj dominates in the paint

videos.description: Frank Howard tosses a no-look pass to Oshae Brissett who throws down the two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Cuse's Brissett slams home emphatic dunk
